node.text:
Happy #WorldElephantDay ❤️🐘• 

@theellenfund Contrary to what you may have heard, elephants are not afraid of mice, though they are scared of bees. Because of this, some African farmers protect their fields from elephant damage by lining the borders with beehives. Link in bio! ❤️🐝🐘 📸: Independent birds #triviathursday #elephant #conservation #bees #WorldElephantDay #elephantfacts

node.text: I’m so proud of my wife for creating this company and for doing so well at RH. She has grown this business from an idea to a company. Link in bio for the page in RH and check out Generalpublic.art and GeneralPublicArt.com for more.

node.text: Probably because I’m not the one helping him.

We love family reunions on our show! Vrbo has been running a summer promotion all about family reunions and there are just 8 days left to enter! They’re giving away 1 family reunion trip every day through August 12th! Go to @Vrbo to find out how to enter.
